org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart.MultipartHttpServletRequest

  • MultipartHttpServletRequestを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart
    commons fileupload跟Servlet3.0内置上传功能的包装与实现 Multipart resolution framework for handling file uploads.
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart.commons
    MultipartResolver implementation for Apache Commons FileUpload.
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart.support
    Support classes for the multipart resolution framework.

    • org.sxb.upload.ext.multipartでのMultipartHttpServletRequestの使用

      MultipartHttpServletRequestを返すorg.sxb.upload.ext.multipartのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      MultipartHttpServletRequest MultipartResolver.resolveMultipart(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
      Parse the given HTTP request into multipart files and parameters, and wrap the request inside a org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartHttpServletRequest object that provides access to file descriptors and makes contained parameters accessible via the standard ServletRequest methods.
      MultipartHttpServletRequest型のパラメータを持つorg.sxb.upload.ext.multipartのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      void MultipartResolver.cleanupMultipart(MultipartHttpServletRequest request)
      Cleanup any resources used for the multipart handling, like a storage for the uploaded files.
